headline.print_headline: Libyan Official: US Navy Hands Oil Tanker to Libya
headline.main: Libyan Official: US Navy Hands Oil Tanker to Libya

lead_paragraph: American sailors handed over control of a captured North Korean-flagged oil tanker to Libyan forces while in international waters Saturday, a spokesman for the Libyan navy said.
